data.description: *Eligible Veterans can assume 4.25% VA loan* Don't wait to build, this less than 2 year old home has a bright open floorplan with large greatroom/dining room with stone fireplace. Kitchen has granite counter tops, large island with bar, walkin pantry and comes complete with smart appliances including refrigerator, gas cook top, builtin oven and microwave. Owner's suite has walkin closet and bath with dual sink vanity, garden tub and separate shower. Two additional bedrooms and bath separate from owner's bedroom. Home has a flex room, ideal for home office or den. Backyard has low maintenance landscaping with covered and open patios with solar lights, mountain and city views plus a putting green. Additional features include water softener, high ceilings, 8 ft doors and full house gutters.
